Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了莉菲雅後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.89,0:00:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又得知哥哥艾俄洛斯早已被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歐里亞在絕望之中一度身陷險境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此時 將其救下的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,童虎 撒加和穆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與此同時 馳援而至的沙加指出了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德烈亞斯的真實身份就是邪神洛基的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基的目的是吸取黃金聖鬥士的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使邪惡果實在這片大地上復活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　Athena Exclamation\N{\r}憑藉著神聖衣的力量 以雅典娜之驚歎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一舉消滅了安德烈亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:01:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎成功阻止了洛基的完全復活…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我自己得救了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖衣被…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪惡的果實之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼東西就要誕生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想辦法阻止它的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那果實已從12件黃金聖衣中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及仙宮的大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸取了足以讓它成熟的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無人可擋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復活！仙宮的邪神洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德烈亞斯大人到底在做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾正是仙宮之神 洛基！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾將代替奧丁主宰這片大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荒謬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜之驚歎 應該已經阻止了你的復活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若吾的棲身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那個男人的肉體的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必也是極難復活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾早已另有準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件斗衣 就是吾的另一處棲身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到邪神洛基竟能完全復活…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待到那朵花蕾綻放之時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之野心便會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你如願的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在果實完全成熟之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會打倒你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然還有力氣戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能獨自一人從世界之樹中成功逃脫也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你區區一介人類能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何況是在這種失去聖衣的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你甚至不可能觸碰到吾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄抵抗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命被人玩弄於掌中 自己卻束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就懊悔著自己的無力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次赴死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金色的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃金聖衣正在哭泣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了如此不成器的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃金聖衣竟流下了眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖衣流淚？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無稽之談
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動 動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徹徹底底的絕望已在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻仍然不願正視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而沉浸於名為希望的幻想之中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類還真是可悲的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是艾俄洛斯哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你變堅強了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只剩下孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也堅持戰鬥至此 幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 從現在起你不再是孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射手座
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖失去了聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻被瓦拉哈拉宮的人所救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受了治療
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Polaris　　　　\N{\r}之後我從北極星的希路達那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知了一切的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也包括安德烈亞斯的真身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是邪神洛基一事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來希路達已經察覺到吾的真身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北極星的希路達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基 我最初便清楚你的所有企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 從封印之中被解放的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依附在宮廷醫師安德烈亞斯·裡瑟的肉體之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待著在這片大地上完全復活的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於 雅典娜與哈迪斯的戰火燃起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為這是將地上據為己有的絕好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這座仙宮之中 卻有個名為奧丁的眼中釘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是在這時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基你打算利用在冥界犧牲的12名黃金聖鬥士的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那種被譽為可匹敵太陽的聖衣之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使世界之樹的果實 孕育出毀滅性的恐怖力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毀滅性的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙宮傳說中的究極神器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Gungnir\N{\r}永恆之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此 希路達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能夠得到永恆之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧丁之流便不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不會讓你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別慌 艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:10:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在永恆之槍誕生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒洛基便可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為區區人類能辦到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何況是在沒有黃金聖衣的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們能成什麼事！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強弱並不由所穿的聖衣決定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能將自身蘊藏的小宇宙爆發到何種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此一點才是關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小宇宙也產生了共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙 是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何都至少要保護希路達大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希路達大人 這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基所操縱的死者的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英靈戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Paal De Bril\N{\r}北極閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西格蒙德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亡者們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你們碰希路達大人分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我神鬥士格拉尼的西格蒙德還站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的拳中甦醒吧 獅子之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Lightning Plasma\N{\r}等離子光速拳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的拳啊 化為正義之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誅殺邪惡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Atomic Thunder Bolt\N{\r}原子雷電光速拳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苟延殘喘的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有靈魂的士兵 無論來多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是我們的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要掉以輕心 艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果實很快就要成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也差不多該讓你們消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類們 消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先暫且退後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的仙宮之神奧丁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請傾聽我們這些侍奉奧丁的神鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和仙宮子民的聲音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾俄洛斯哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著 艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算落入敵人的陷阱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論暴露出怎樣的醜態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們聖鬥士的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都並不是由此決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:16:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經 我不懼背負逆賊的污名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便遭到追殺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要拯救雅典娜的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為我心中有唯一的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信念？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次也是同樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了正在冥界戰鬥的年輕聖鬥士們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們決不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們用這新的生命應該做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是讓生命延續到下一個世代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這反應是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:52.80,remark,NTP,0,0,0,,Draupnir，北歐神話中奧丁擁有的每九天就會自行複製一次的指環或臂環，也被稱為「聚金指環」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是擁有著足以封印邪神力量的寶具「德羅普尼爾」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射手座啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了這德羅普尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定能夠再次封印洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但據說 如果不被德羅普尼爾所認同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便無法發揮出它真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德羅普尼爾正和你的小宇宙產生共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花就快要開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恆之槍就將為吾所有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決不會讓永恆之槍落入你手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此急於求死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如你所願 讓你的性命斷絕於此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用這拳讓你回歸虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 剛才的力量是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德羅普尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到竟然藏著那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彫蟲小技
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}Lightning Plasma\N{\r}等離子光速拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不被德羅普尼爾直接擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的區區攻擊算不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會逃跑的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的武器不就白費了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心 艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知分寸的愚蠢人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾俄洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們堅持不懈 戰鬥至此 值得嘉獎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 這個龐大的小宇宙是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於覺醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙宮的偉大神明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧丁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟是奧丁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是仙宮之神 奧丁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲亞竟然是奧丁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的驚訝也是無可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲雅正是接替希路達大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被授予了奧丁之力的地上代行者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烏特迦從很早以前就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德烈亞斯的真實身份是邪神洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 奧丁要在新的地上代行者身上完全覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還需要一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那時為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都必須在洛基眼皮底下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25}　　　　　　　　　　　　　Odin Robe\N{\r}將終有一日要派上用場的奧丁斗衣隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烏特迦自絕性命化身英靈戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借此將奧丁斗衣隱藏在了自己體內
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在根據奧丁神的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被指名選擇為守護仙宮的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被奧丁選中？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被選中的並非仙宮中人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是你 此事實在令人遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 艾歐里亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧丁神會認同你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就說明你毫無疑問是真正的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓永恆之槍在這片大地上復活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 就與這把劍一同戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這道光是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧丁斗衣披掛在了艾歐里亞身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧丁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我獅子座的艾歐里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實接收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被托付了奧丁斗衣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾歐里亞與邪神洛基展開激戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 聖鬥士星矢 黃金魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誕生！神器永恆之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎
